title: STUCK on the bottom of the Ocean | Sal Vulcano & Chris Distefano Present: Hey Babe! | EP 81
description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES!
This week the babes talk about what really makes you a bad dancer. What is dancing? Parents teach you to be insecure before anyone else. Chris got invited on Dancing with The Stars. Chris is all about that backyard summer lifestyle! Sal almost pukes at Chris new weird bedroom habit. Seasonal Allergies are hell! How many time zones are there? Milk is SUS. Bad sleep habits add up. Chris breaks down the last breath documentary. What would you do trapped at the bottom of the ocean.
